Uncle Waffles has poured cold water over rumours that she is transgender. This after the DJ, whose real name is Lungelihle Zwane, was seen posing for a photo with her dancers during the Cotton Fest in Johannesburg at the weekend. The photo caused a stir on social media about Uncle Waffles’ gender, with many people taking to Twitter to body-shame the DJ. Read the comments below:     The DJ responded to her tormenters by saying she does not have to prove her gender because of her physique. She wrote: “Instead you’re trying to bring down people who have nothing to do with this. I now have to prove my gender based on my physique and based on a rumour? You guys are so weird.”     Also Read: Uncle Waffles ecstatic after shout-out from Drake For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.